init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is the story of a group of young people who must learn to master their new powers, and their enemies, before the world is destroyed

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was born in a world where magic was a thing of the past.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The power of mana was returning.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked at the plant on my desk and noticed it was growing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I looked at my hands and noticed a faint glow.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was lucky enough to bond with this one.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I knew that I had to help the humans fight back against the aliens.
